data.title: Kentucky Players in the Pros
data.text:
Kentucky Players Who Were Drafted or Played in the NBA

151 Players Drafted; 124 Players Played

Note: provides an external link to the player's professional statistics in the NBA (and/or ABA).

* denotes that the player was on the NBA roster, but did not see any action that season. Players with an (**) transferred to Kentucky prior to being drafted or playing. Players with an (***) transferred from Kentucky prior to being drafted or playing. Players with a (LE) declared early for the pros and left the program before they used all their eligibility at UK.

Players who were drafted as junior-eligible players but returned to school (thus making the selection null and void) are noted but not double-counted.
